The prim. Germ. forms of ansts were:
Sing. nom. *anstiz, acc. *anstin, voc. *ansti, gen. *anstaiz (= Indg. -eĩs, -oĩs), dat. *anstēi (originally the loc. ending);
Pl. nom. *anstīz (older -ijiz = Indg. -ejes, cp. Skr. tráyas, Gr. τρεῖς from *τρέ(j)ες, three);
